  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Clean and maintain guest rooms according to set standards and procedure Responds timely to guests’ special request for miscellaneous items like cribs, cots, extra towels, etc</li><li>Follows departmental policies and procedures.</li><li>Adhere to personal grooming and hygiene standards</li><li>Any other duties as may be assigned from time to time.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Able to perform basic cleaning duties and relevant experience a plus</li><li>Highly responsible & reliable</li><li>Willingness to perform shifts</li></ul>",
